title: A New York 6
description: Jay was at the 76er’s game 6 playoffs and was amazed at what all the rich white guys were yelling at the players. After a power lunch with Comedy Central executives, Jay is bummed that Dan is the belle of the ball at Del Frisco’s from wide eyed fans.  The crew ranks themselves on a scale of 1 to 10.  Jay is dissed by a cab driver who is a big fan of Dave Attell but doesn’t know who he is.
author: podcasts@siriusxm.com (Comedy Central)
